        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Safe Stay Act</b><br /><br />This bill requires places of public accommodation to install compliant carbon monoxide detectors within each sleeping or dwelling unit. Further, during check-in, such accommodations must provide each guest with written notice of compliance with the requirement. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
