    <title>Safe Stay Act</title>
    <titles>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Federal Fire Prevention and Control Act of 1974 to update the fire prevention and control guidelines to require the mandatory installation of carbon monoxide alarms in all places of public accommodation, and for other purposes.</title>
